WEBVTT

00:01.567 --> 00:04.085
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.120 --> 00:07.355
(phone ringing)

00:08.890 --> 00:10.858
(answering machine clicks)

00:10.859 --> 00:12.827
WOODY (over machine):
Hi, this is Cheers.

00:12.828 --> 00:15.463
Well, it isn't actually Cheers,
it's Woody Boyd.

00:15.464 --> 00:16.697
Cheers is actually the bar,

00:16.698 --> 00:18.733
and as such,
it couldn't be expected to talk.

00:18.734 --> 00:20.201
SAM:
Woody, start again.

00:20.236 --> 00:21.802
WOODY:
Why? I'm doing fine.

00:21.837 --> 00:24.872
Anyway, uh, there's no one here
to take your call right now.

00:24.873 --> 00:26.341
Well, actually,
if you called right now,

00:26.342 --> 00:28.476
we could take your call,
but if you call when you're...

00:28.477 --> 00:29.977
SAM:
Woody, would you cut it out?

00:29.978 --> 00:30.978
It's sounding stupid.

00:30.979 --> 00:31.979
WOODY:
I am not.

00:31.980 --> 00:33.148
W-W-Why do you always treat me

00:33.149 --> 00:34.215
like I don't know
what I'm doing?

00:34.216 --> 00:35.316
SAM:
It sounds stupid, Woody.

00:35.317 --> 00:36.884
WOODY:
It does not.

00:36.918 --> 00:38.753
(machine beeps)

00:38.787 --> 00:40.155
Hi, Sam, this is Woody.

00:40.189 --> 00:41.789
Uh, I guess you were right.

00:41.823 --> 00:44.425
It does sound stupid.

00:44.460 --> 00:45.926
I'll change it tomorrow.

00:45.961 --> 00:47.962
(theme song begins)

00:51.901 --> 00:54.185
♪ Making your way
in the world today ♪

00:54.220 --> 00:57.405
♪ Takes everything you've got ♪

00:57.439 --> 01:00.074
♪ Taking a break
from all your worries ♪

01:00.109 --> 01:03.495
♪ Sure would help a lot ♪

01:03.529 --> 01:07.616
♪ Wouldn't you like
to get away? ♪

01:08.851 --> 01:11.219
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:11.253 --> 01:15.640
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:16.875 --> 01:21.379
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:21.413 --> 01:23.848
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:23.882 --> 01:26.417
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:26.452 --> 01:30.588
♪ You wanna be where
everybody knows your name ♪

01:31.790 --> 01:33.891
♪ You wanna go
where people know ♪

01:33.925 --> 01:36.927
♪ People are all the same ♪

01:36.962 --> 01:41.732
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

